[[Image:Salami aka.jpg|right|thumb|Salami]]

'''Salami''' is a popular type of [[Cookbook:Fermentation|fermented]] [[cookbook:sausage|sausage]] made usually of [[Cookbook:Pork|pork]] and [[Cookbook:Beef|beef]]. It is most popular in cold cut sandwiches, but may also be used as a snack or a [[Cookbook:Pizza|pizza]] topping.

