u}\,\Gamma \left( rac{
u}{2}ight)} \end{matrix}</math><br/ >where <sub>2</sub>''F''<sub>1</sub> is the [[hypergeometric function]]| mean =0 for ν > 1, otherwise [[indeterminate form|undefined]]| median =0| mode =0| variance =<math>	extstyle rac{
u}{
u-2}</math> for ν > 2, ∞ for 1 < ν ≤ 2, otherwise [[indeterminate form|undefined]]| skewness =0 for ν > 3, otherwise [[indeterminate form|undefined]]| kurtosis =<math>	extstyle rac{6}{
u-4}</math> for ν > 4, ∞ for 2 < ν ≤ 4, otherwise [[indeterminate form|undefined]]| entropy =...| | mgf = undefined| char =<math>	extstyle rac{K_{
